<div style="font-size:18px; border-bottom:1px solid #000; margin:20px 0px 5px 0px; padding:0px 0px 5px 0px;">Introduction</div>
Last Summoner is a Tactical Medal RPG Browser game on DMM.com. The game features girls gaining powers from "Brave Souls", including Oda Nobunaga and King Arthur.
* <span style="font-size:16px;">[http://www.dmm.com/netgame/social/-/gadgets/=/app_id=159001/ '''Game is online!''']</span>. Since launch, servers did not experience technical difficulties. Maintenance times are mostly followed.
* <span style="font-size:16px;">[http://lastsummoner.wikia.com '''Wikia is updated''']</span>, fully-setup to get your started playing! It is maintained by an active team of players. Anyone can contribute!

